---
/**
 * Retro mode banner — present in the DOM on every page in both modes (re-skin,
 * not re-layout: see src/styles/retro.css .retro-mode-banner rules), hidden by
 * default and revealed only in retro. One of the two always-present exits back
 * to modern (the other is the toast in AppearanceToast.astro).
 */
---

<div class="retro-mode-banner" role="region" aria-label="Appearance mode notice">
  You are in <strong>retro mode</strong>.
  <button type="button" id="appearance-exit">Back to modern</button>
</div>
